Description: Wonderfully cared for guitar from smoke free household. Beautiful looks and sound with a great feeling neck, frets and fretboard. Here's a link from PRS and the description (by the way these sell at $799 new). The SE Zach Myers has enough features to satisfy even the most demanding musicians. The resonance of the semi-hollow body paired with the smooth feel of the satin finish neck will make an immediate impression in your hands. "I’ve been with PRS for 12 years. This is the best guitar I have ever played," – Zach Myers, Shinedown. Additional appointments to the SE Zach Myers signature model include PRS adjustable stoptail bridge, vintage style tuners, and PRS SE 245 pickups paired with two volume and two tone controls and a 3-way toggle pickup switch.
